{"tid":747474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"玩股票(畀股票玩) 之後對你既生活有咩改變？","createTime":"2018-07-18T11:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T00:24:23.000Z","uid":57308,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"167464bf1b80eee6d090426b58948bdfb7cfdcfe","tid":747474,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"輸到仆街，換手機只夠錢換紅米，個垃圾mon搞到我對眼近視深左又有散光，仲成日好乾<br />\n以前用htc同sony對眼都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有排玩牛熊(畀牛熊玩)  搞到我失眠，成撚日睇住個市，搞到俾公司個老屎忽屌，心情又變得好差<br />\n嗰排真係日日lunch唔係食杯麵就係去7仔食叮飯，想慳啲儲錢繼續炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家用輸淨既錢all in左一隻，心情好左，又唔洗成日心掛掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767c0a2ae48f9a58dd959f3b9678305423201420","tid":747474,"uid":57308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"上年既7月開始入市俾股票玩，嗰陣qq日日升，真係求其入隻牛都賺到仆街<br />\n之後騰爆，房爆，紙爆全部俾我中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再到1月定唔記得2月一日跌千鳩幾點嗰日追熊，又再一次輸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c22b719ab764b06b52dc729a427b4493992aee8","tid":747474,"uid":176875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167464bf1b80eee6d090426b58948bdfb7cfdcfe","tid":747474,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"輸到仆街，換手機只夠錢換紅米，個垃圾mon搞到我對眼近視深左又有散光，仲成日好乾<br />\n以前用htc同sony對眼都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif